# Overview

This charm provides the Arista ML2 Mechanism neutron plugin for OpenStack clouds.

# Usage

This charm is subordinate to the **neutron-api** charm.

You must set manage-neutron-plugin-legacy-mode in your neutron-api
charm's config to False before deploying this charm.

Instruction for deploying the charm:

*    juju config neutron-api manage-neutron-plugin-legacy-mode=False
*    juju deploy neutron-api-arista
*    juju add-relation neutron-api neutron-api-arista

